\change_unchanged
) 
\change_inserted -1666014648 1589337407
GWAS Execution in the for packages using 
\change_deleted -1666014648 1589334015
the execution of 
\change_unchanged
two GWAS models, the full model with control for population structure and
 individual relatedness and the Naive model without any control
\change_inserted -1666014648 1589337446
