\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
\align center
\begin_inset Caption Standard

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Timeline for articles reported for GWAS studies on polyploid species in
 PubMed.
 We present data for completed years.
\begin_inset CommandInset label
